        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 lead px-5">
          <p>We are a small group of students working at Bushwick Generator, a “community-led innovation lab”
            that aims to introduce modern technology into new industries for a better future. <b>We have chosen
              to create a project centered around improving schools, especially in neighborhoods where there may be
              a disconnect between students, parents, and teachers.</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>
